Prepare @Chess Pie{1}.

Add 2/3 cup additional @white sugar{2/3%cup} and us 2/3 cup @buttermilk{2/3%cup} instead of cream or milk.

Stir into the filling chopped @pecans or walnuts (optional){1/2%cup} and chopped @raisins (optional){1/2%cup}.

Bake until the center is set when nudged, 35 to ~{40%minutes}.
